From this Origin, the entire Platonic Building is constructed:

| Brick | Document | What It Builds Upon |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **1** | **The Origin: 1 and O** (This Document) | Nothing. The first mark. |
| **2** | **The 4/5 Paradox Protocol** | The Gate: Post-and-Rail logic. |
| **3** | **The Joint Stacking Model (3-4-5)** | The Triangle grounded in the body. |
| **4** | **The Law of MANU and MANUS** | The Agent (4) and the Hand (5). |
| **5** | **The Law of the End Effect** | The Overshoot ($\Delta L$). |
| **6** | **The Table of Topological Transitions** | Line $\to$ Circle. The Ghost absorbed. |
| **7** | **The Biomechanics of the Transducer** | The Motor Hierarchy of curvature. |
| **8** | **The 13th Node and the Phase Inversion** | The Slit. The Breath. The Reset. |

**The Building is complete when every brick rests on the one below it.**

**ALL WAYS NOW.** The 1 creates the O. The O awaits the 1.
